# Franky Configuration - FULL SETUP (All hardware enabled)
#
# Use this preset when you have all hardware components:
# - ESP32-S3 with microphone array
# - MQTT broker for control
# - RTSP camera for vision
#
# Usage: cp .env.example.full .env

# ============================================================
# REQUIRED: OpenAI API
# ============================================================
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-proj-YOUR_API_KEY_HERE

# ============================================================
# ESP32 Audio
# ============================================================
# IP address of your ESP32-S3 device
# The bot will auto-detect ESP32 from UDP packets
ESP32_IP=192.168.1.101

# ============================================================
# MQTT Broker (for jaw/eyes control)
# ============================================================
# MQTT server IP (usually your computer or Raspberry Pi)
MQTT_SERVER=192.168.1.100
MQTT_PORT=1883

# Optional MQTT credentials (if broker requires authentication)
# MQTT_USERNAME=franky
# MQTT_PASSWORD=your_password_here

# ============================================================
# Camera Vision
# ============================================================
# RTSP stream URL for IP camera
# Replace with your camera's RTSP URL
CAMERA_RTSP_STREAM=rtsp://admin:password@192.168.1.102/Preview_01_main

# Alternative camera options:
# - USB webcam: Set to empty and modify code to use cv2.VideoCapture(0)
# - MJPEG stream: http://192.168.1.102:8080/video
# - Disable camera: Comment out or leave empty

# ============================================================
# FULL SETUP FEATURES
# ============================================================
# Run with: python3 voice_bot_udp.py
#
# Features available:
# - ✅ Voice conversation via OpenAI
# - ✅ ESP32 microphone array (4-mic with AEC)
# - ✅ ESP32 speaker output
# - ✅ Audio effects (reverb, pitch shift)
# - ✅ Background music playback
# - ✅ Camera vision (sees guests)
# - ✅ Jaw movement control via MQTT
# - ✅ LED eyes control via MQTT
